text: Exclusive: Channel 4 News has seen the inventory of the UK government pandemic PPE stockpile - and can reveal almost 80% of respirators were out of date when coronavirus hit. Watch the full investigation at 7pm tonight on Channel 4 News. https://t.co/0DrdIodTnr
